{"title":"Transition Scout & Sentinel MTBs gain affordable alloy options","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/21/transition-roll-out-more-affordable-aluminium-frame-builds-of-sentinel-and-scout-mtbs/","date":1632236420000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"alloy transition scout mtb frame\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071926/transition-scout-alloy-frame-275-mtb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-272125\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Transition Bikes have released alloy builds of the long-travel 29er Sentinel and 27.5″ Scout Trail bike. Previously available in carbon only, the new NX and GX builds will retail at a much more budget-friendly price of $3899 USD and $4999 USD, respectively, with framesets only available too.</p><h2>Transition Sentinel and Scout Alloy Builds</h2><div id=\"attachment_272169\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-272169\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue.jpg\" alt=\"alloy transition sentinel 29er\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071930/transition-sentinel-29er-alloy-full-suspension-mtb-blue-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-272169\">The 29″ <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/04/28/2021-transition-sentinel-29er-trail-bike-gets-150mm-out-back-w-updated-leverage-curve/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Transition Sentinel</a> gets 150mm rear wheel travel paired with a 160mm fork sat at a 63.6° head angle</p></div><p>Those who prefer the reliability and durability of an aluminum mountain bike frame will be pleased to hear that the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/04/28/2021-transition-sentinel-29er-trail-bike-gets-150mm-out-back-w-updated-leverage-curve/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Transition Sentinel</a> and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/02/13/transition-scout-carbon-2020-receives-geometry-overhaul-adjustable-rear-travel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Scout</a> full suspension bikes are now available as alloy framesets. Both get the same Speed Balanced Geometry of their carbon counterparts, but at a more affordable price point you might expect from the heavier aluminum frame.</p><div id=\"attachment_272167\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-272167\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb.jpg\" alt=\"alloy transition scout\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20071922/alloy-transition-scout-140mm-travel-mtb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-272167\">The<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/02/13/transition-scout-carbon-2020-receives-geometry-overhaul-adjustable-rear-travel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Transition Scout</a> comes with 140mm rear wheel travel stock, which can be upgraded to 150mm with a longer stroke shock</p></div><p>The Transition Bikes product team have hand-picked a parts list to give riders as much bang for their buck as is possible with two price points for each bike. The NX build ($3899 USD) comes with a FOX 36 Rhythm fork and Float X Performance shock, along with SRAM Code R brakes and the SRAM NX 12 speed drivetrain, of course.</p><div id=\"attachment_272170\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-272170\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"873\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black-297x162.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black-800x437.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black-120x65.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black-768x419.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072607/transition-scout-alloy-frame-black-1536x838.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-272170\">The Transition Scout Alloy NX build is available in Black and Raspberry colorways</p></div><p>The GX build is particularly attractive given the $4999 USD asking price. It moves up to a FOX 36 Performance Elite fork with the GRIP 2 damper and Float X Performance Elite Shock, DT Swiss M 1900 wheelset, powerful SRAM Code RSC brakes, finished off with an ANVL cockpit. There’s nothing on that build that needs upgraded*. Both models include Maxxis Assegai 3C EXO+ / Maxxis Minion DHRII 3C EXO+ tires (*I’d probably swap this out for a DoubleDown), and a OneUP dropper post.</p><div id=\"attachment_272171\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-272171\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame.jpg\" alt=\"transition sentinel alloy silver nx build\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame-297x241.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame-800x650.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame-120x98.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame-768x624.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20072611/transition-sentinel-silver-nx-build-alloy-frame-1536x1248.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-272171\">The Transition Sentinel Alloy NX build is available in Silver and Blue colorways</p></div><p>The aluminium Transition Scout and Sentinel bikes both come with a lifetime warranty. The frames run Enduro Max Sealed Bearings with bearing shields on the main pivot, a threaded Bottom Bracket and a 44/56mm press-in headset.</p><p>Both bikes get molded rubber chainstay, seatstay, and downtube protectors. Cable routing is internal, save for the rear brake hose. There’s also room to store a water bottle inside the front triangle and an accessory mounting point on the underside of the top tube.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.transitionbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>TransitionBikes.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9c6c3434f341805cdb89f76e0e60190a9b1d80e0258cf1a95a55f2cdbad57772","category":"Cycling"}